{"tid":1360883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我重申一次： 宜家係六種勢力互相勾結","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:38:44.000Z","uid":112433,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05b5a14c0258d9a0a6b7c564e6669f6179966d31","tid":1360883,"uid":112433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 官</span></span><br />\n不用多說 永遠追究 殺人兇手 林鄭 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 商</span></span><br />\n沙田一役 商場經理收到指示引清兵入關 <br />\n且令無辜市民為指嚇及受傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 鄉</span></span><br />\n港英政府流下嘅新界癌 <br />\n有恃無恐 同 警察合作無間 鄉即黑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 警</span></span><br />\n由609開始作為港共政權嘅工具<br />\n嚴重傷害無數無辜市民 <br />\n沒有一個黑警是無辜的<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 鐵</span></span><br />\n仆街港鐵721 當日完全喺知情之下 <br />\n置乘客安危於不顧 可見<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鐵黑合作</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6. 黑</span></span><br />\n黑社會只係收錢做嘢嘅戲子 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">始作俑者仍然未浮面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無懼鄉黑 727 元朗見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8e428c9c9244dbdaa5e1a3a4cc456b8386964a","tid":1360883,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"傳媒呢？"},